{"title":"OsStart","date":"2022-01-28T16:48:58.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年1月28日","L":"2022/01/28","MM-DD":"01-28"},"link":"2022/01/28/OsStart","categories":["操作系统"],"updated":"2022-02-21T09:53:10.898Z","content":"<h1 id=\"操作系统的启动\">操作系统的启动<a title=\"#操作系统的启动\" href=\"#操作系统的启动\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"从图灵机到通用图灵机\">从图灵机到通用图灵机<a title=\"#从图灵机到通用图灵机\" href=\"#从图灵机到通用图灵机\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"从通用图灵机到计算机\">从通用图灵机到计算机<a title=\"#从通用图灵机到计算机\" href=\"#从通用图灵机到计算机\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart1.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"x86pc的开机过程\">x86PC的开机过程<a title=\"#x86pc的开机过程\" href=\"#x86pc的开机过程\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>开机时，CS=0xFFFF; IP=0x0000（和保护模式对应，实模式的寻址CS:IP(CS左移4位+IP)，和保护模式不一样）</li>\n<li>寻址0xFFFF0(ROM BIOS映射区)（0xFFFF0 = CS &lt;&lt; 4 + IP）</li>\n<li>检查RAM，键盘，显示器，软硬磁盘（检查是否有硬件损坏）</li>\n<li>将磁盘0磁道0扇区读入0x7c00处</li>\n<li>设置CS=0x07c0, IP=0x0000</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart2.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<hr>\n<aside>\n💡 0x7c00处存放的代码就是从磁盘引导扇区读入的那512个字节\n</aside>\n<ul>\n<li>引导扇区就是启动设备的第一个扇区</li>\n<li>启动设备信息被设置在CMOS中</li>\n<li>因此，磁盘的第一个扇区存放着开机后执行的第一段我们可以控制的程序</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）\">引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）<a title=\"#引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）\" href=\"#引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>bootsect.s首先把自己从内存0x7c00的位置挪到0x90000的位置，为后续读入OS代码腾空间。然后从磁盘将setup程序（占4个扇区）读入内存0x90200，然后打印开机logo（如system is loading…，logo可修改，如下图），然后调用13号中断，继续读入system模块（OS代码）。bootsect.s的功能就结束了。bootsect.s的最后一行跳转到了setup所在的0x90200位置，开始执行setup程序</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart3.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<aside>\n💡 BOOTSEG = 0x07c0\nINITSEG = 0x9000\nSETUPSEG = 0x9020\n</aside>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.globl begtext,begdata,begbss,endtext,enddata,endbss</span><br><span class=\"line\">.text  //文本段</span><br><span class=\"line\">begtext:</span><br><span class=\"line\">.data  //数据段</span><br><span class=\"line\">begdata:</span><br><span class=\"line\">.bss   //未初始化数据段</span><br><span class=\"line\">begbss:</span><br><span class=\"line\">entry start //关键字entry告诉链接器“程序入口”</span><br><span class=\"line\">start:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #BOOTSEG</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #INITSEG</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov es, ax </span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov cx, #256</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sub si, si</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sub di, di</span><br><span class=\"line\">  rep movw //到这里上面语句的作用就是将0x07c0:0x0000处的256个字（512字节）移动到0x9000:0x0000处</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jmpi go, INITSEG //跳转到地址INITSEG:go处</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">go:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, cs //cs = 0x9000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov es, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ss. ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov sp, #0xff00</span><br><span class=\"line\">load_setup: //载入setup模块</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov dx, #0x0000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov cx, #0x0002</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov bx, #0x0200</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #0x0200+SETUPLEN</span><br><span class=\"line\">  int 0x13 //利用0x13中断将四个setup扇区读入，0x13的详细解释请见[https://wenku.baidu.com/view/71d73e460c22590103029d58.html?re=view](https://wenku.baidu.com/view/71d73e460c22590103029d58.html?re=view)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jnc ok_load_setup//如果0x13中断读取有错误会在CF位上置位，所以如果未置位就可以正常跳转到ok_load_setup函数处执行，所以这里要用jnc跳转</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov dx. #0x0000//如果上面的0x13中断执行错误，就复位驱动器再来一遍</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #0x0000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  int 0x13</span><br><span class=\"line\">  j   load_setup//又跳回到上面重新来循环</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart4.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup\">读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup<a title=\"#读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup\" href=\"#读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Ok_load_setip: //载入setup模块</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov dl, #0x00</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #0x800 //ah=8获得磁盘参数</span><br><span class=\"line\">  int 0x13</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ch, #0x00</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov sectors, cx</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ah, 0x03</span><br><span class=\"line\">  xor bh, bh</span><br><span class=\"line\">  [int 0x10](https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/INT_10H) //功能代码ah为0x03，所以这里0x10中断作用为读取光标位置</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov cx, #24</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov bx, #0x0007 //7是属性</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov bp, #msg1</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #1301</span><br><span class=\"line\">  [int 0x10](https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/INT_10H) //功能代码ah为0x13，所以这里0x10中断作用为显示字符，即显示系统logo</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #SYSSEG //SYSSEG=0x1000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov es, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  call read_it //读入system模块</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jmpi 0, SETUPSEG //转入0x9020:0x0000执行setup.s</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<aside>\n💡 bootsect.s中的数据 //在文件末尾\n<p>sectors:  .word  0</p>\n<p>msgl: .byte  13 , 10</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">     .ascii “Loading system...”（开机语句，可修改）</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">.byte 13 , 10 , 13 , 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</aside>\n<h3 id=\"read_it-//读入system模块\">read_it //读入system模块<a title=\"#read_it-//读入system模块\" href=\"#read_it-//读入system模块\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>system模块可能很大，要跨越磁道，所以还要定义一个函数来读入（也是用0x13中断来读）</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">read_it:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, es</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cmp ax, #ENDSEG</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jb ok1_read</span><br><span class=\"line\">ok1_read:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, sectors</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sub ax, sread //sread是当前磁道已读扇区数，ax未读扇区数</span><br><span class=\"line\">  call read_track //读磁道</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>引导扇区的末尾 //BIOS用以识别引导扇区</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.org 510</span><br><span class=\"line\">  .word 0xAA55 //扇区的最后两个字节</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>可以转入setup执行了。jmpi 0, SETUPSRG</li>\n</ul>\n<aside>\n💡 以上均为bootsect.s,即引导扇区（第一个扇区）所做的所有内容\n</aside>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"setup模块，即setup.s\">setup模块，即setup.s<a title=\"#setup模块，即setup.s\" href=\"#setup模块，即setup.s\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>根据名字就可以想到：setup将完成OS启动前的设置</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">start:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #INITSEG //INITSEG=0x9000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ah, #0x03</span><br><span class=\"line\">  xor bh, bh</span><br><span class=\"line\">  int 0x10 //功能代码ah为0x03，所以这里0x10中断作用为读取光标位置</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov [0], dx //上面0x10中断取出的光标位置的行列号存储在dx，这里取出光标位置（包括其他硬件参数）到0x90000（因为ds=0x9000,这里的地址为9000:0）处</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ah, #0x88</span><br><span class=\"line\">  int 0x15//功能代码ah为0x88,所里这里0x15中断作用为获取连续内存大小，输出结过存储在ax里面</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov [2], ax //扩展内存大小（最开始的内存只有1M，后面的2G，4G都叫扩展内存），并将内存大小写入ds:2</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cli ///禁止中断发生，在CLI起效之后，所有外部中断都被屏蔽，这样可以保证当前运行的代码不被打断，起到保护代码运行的作用</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #0x0000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cld //将标志位DF置为0，使之后rep指令时每次操作后si，di递增</span><br><span class=\"line\">do_move:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov es, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  add ax, #0x1000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cmp ax, #0x9000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jz end_move //转移完则跳转到end_move函数运行</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sub di, di</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sub si, si</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov cx, #0x8000</span><br><span class=\"line\">  rep movsw //将system模块移到0地址</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jmp do_move</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart5.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">end_move</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ax, #SETUPSEG</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  lidt idt_48</span><br><span class=\"line\">  lgdt gdt_48 //设置保护模式下的中断和寻址</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">idt_48:.word 0  .word 0,0 //保护模式中断函数表</span><br><span class=\"line\">gdt_48:.word 0x800  .word 512+gdt, 0x9</span><br><span class=\"line\">gdt:.word 0,0,0,0 </span><br><span class=\"line\">    .word 0x7F00, 0x0000, 0x9A00, 0x00C0</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .word 0x07FF, 0x0000, 0x9200, 0x00C0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"进入保护模式(变为32位，即1m-→-4gb)\">进入保护模式(变为32位，即1M → 4GB)<a title=\"#进入保护模式(变为32位，即1m-→-4gb)\" href=\"#进入保护模式(变为32位，即1m-→-4gb)\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在实模式下我们只能访问1M的内存（也就是说这时能访问的最大内存地址是0xfffff，当我们想要访问0x100000的时候，cpu帮我们环绕到0x0处），所以为了获得更大的内存，我们必须开启<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/A20%E6%80%BB%E7%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\">A20地址线</a>（A20地址线默认禁止），否则我们依旧只能访问1M内存</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>向i8042发送命令:</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>我们需要先把命令发送到0x64端口，</li>\n<li>然后紧接着把这个命令的参数发送到0x60端口，</li>\n<li>然后我们可以通过读0x60端口，获得i8042返回给我们的数据。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">call empty_8042 //测试8042状态寄存器，等待输入缓冲器空，只有当输入缓冲器空才可以对其执行写命令</span><br><span class=\"line\">mov al, #0xD1 //0xD1命令码——表示要写数据到8042的P2端口。P2端口的位1用于A20线的选通，数据要写到0x60端口</span><br><span class=\"line\">out #0x64, al //将al的值写入64端口</span><br><span class=\"line\">//8042是键盘控制器，其输出端口P2用来控制A20地址线</span><br><span class=\"line\">call\tempty_8042 //等待输入缓冲器空，看命令是否被接受</span><br><span class=\"line\">mov\tal,#0xDF\t\t! A20 on</span><br><span class=\"line\">out\t#0x60,al</span><br><span class=\"line\">call\tempty_8042 //若输入缓冲器为空，则表示A20线已选通</span><br><span class=\"line\">//以上均为开启A20地址线的指令</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 初始化8259（中断控制） //一段非常机械化的程序（这里不写）</span><br><span class=\"line\">mov ax, #0x0001</span><br><span class=\"line\">mov cr0, ax //cr0寄存器下面有介绍</span><br><span class=\"line\">jmpi 0, 8 //这里的跳转和实模式下的跳转不同，不可直接直接跳转到8:0，而是根据gdt表项</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">empty_8042:</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \t.word\t0x00eb,0x00eb</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \tin\tal,#0x64\t//从0x64端口读取一字节数据到al</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \ttest\tal,#2\t\t//al &amp; 2结果改变标志寄存器</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \tjnz\tempty_8042\t! 如果al不为0则继续循环，直到al为0时返回（al为0则表示缓冲器为空）</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \tret</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<aside>\n💡 保护模式下int n和cs:ip不再和实模式相同\n</aside>\n<h3 id=\"jmpi-0,-8\">jmpi 0, 8<a title=\"#jmpi-0,-8\" href=\"#jmpi-0,-8\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>首先gdt用.word 0,0,0,0开辟了8个字节的空间，然后又从0x7ff一直到0x00c0又开辟了8个字（16个字节，128位）的空间。所以cs=8就相当于是从0x07ff开始读。</li>\n<li>根据李治军老师的说法+我自己的理解，gdt开辟了8个字节的0空间后，下面又开辟了两个表项，每个表项4个字（8个字节，64位）。所以cs=8相当于选择了第二个表项的内容。第二个表项的内容对照gdt表项的结构来读取我们的</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>0x00c0</th>\n<th>0x9a00</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>0x0000</td>\n<td>0x07ff</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart6.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>第二层是表项的31~0位，第一层是表项的63~32位，这样，段基址15~0位=0x0000,段基址23~16=0x00(也就是0x9a00的低8位)，段基址的31~24位就是0x00(0x00c0的高8位)，所以，读到的基地址就是0x00000000</li>\n<li>最后，由于ip=0，所以最终会跳转到内存中的地址0处</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"cr0寄存器\">cr0寄存器<a title=\"#cr0寄存器\" href=\"#cr0寄存器\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这里就介绍PE和PG位，详细介绍可以看一下<a href=\"http://www.qfrost.com/WindowsKernel/Windows%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0_7/\" target=\"_blank\">Qforst师傅的博客</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>第0位为PE位：<strong>启用保护（Protecction Enable）标志</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>PE=1：保护模式</li>\n<li>PE=0：实地址模式</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<aside>\n💡 这个标志仅开启段级保护，不代表会启用分页机制\n</aside>\n<ul>\n<li>第31位为PG位：<strong>分页机制允许（Paging Enable）标志</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>PG=1：开启了分页机制</li>\n<li>PG=0：未开启分页机制</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>分页机制介绍：<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/3558942fe14f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/3558942fe14f</a></p>\n<aside>\n💡 在开启这个标志位之前必须已经或者同时开启PE标志\n</aside>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart7.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"保护模式下的地址翻译和中断处理\">保护模式下的地址翻译和中断处理<a title=\"#保护模式下的地址翻译和中断处理\" href=\"#保护模式下的地址翻译和中断处理\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>保护模式下的地址翻译</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>即gdt作用</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>t 是table，所以实模式下：cs左移4+ip。保护模式下：根据cs查表+ip</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart8.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>保护模式下中断处理函数入口</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>即idt作用</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>t仍是table，仿照gdt，通过int n的n进行查表</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart9.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"跳到system模块执行\">跳到system模块执行<a title=\"#跳到system模块执行\" href=\"#跳到system模块执行\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>system模块（目标代码）中的第一部分代码是head.s</li>\n<li>Image系统镜像组成：\n<ul>\n<li>boot/bootsect</li>\n<li>boot/setup</li>\n<li>tools/system\n<ul>\n<li>boot/head.o</li>\n<li>init/main.o</li>\n<li>$(DRIVERS)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>tools/build</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"head.s（32位汇编代码）\">head.s（32位汇编代码）<a title=\"#head.s（32位汇编代码）\" href=\"#head.s（32位汇编代码）\"></a></h3>\n<aside>\n💡 一段在保护模式下运行的代码\n</aside>\n<ul>\n<li>setup是进入保护模式，head是进入之后的初始化</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">startup_32:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  movl $0x10,%eax\t/* 段选择子 0b0000 0000 0001 0000，指向 GDT 第三个描述符 */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%ds\t\t/* 描述符在 setup.s 第 213 行，将物理起始地址描述为数据段 */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%es\t\t/* 将这个段选择子载入各个段寄存器 */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%fs</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%gs</span><br><span class=\"line\">  lss stack_start,%esp\t/* 加载堆栈段指针，stack_start 符号定义在 kernel/sched.c 中 */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  call setup_idt\t\t/* 重新设置 IDT */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  call setup_gdt\t\t/* 重新设置 GDT */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  movl $0x10,%eax\t\t/* 修改 GDT 后重新加载一遍段寄存器及堆栈段指针 ss:esp */</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%ds</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%es</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%fs</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mov %ax,%gs</span><br><span class=\"line\">  lss stack_start,%esp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>关于汇编…head.s的汇编和前面不一样</li>\n<li>as86汇编：能产生16位代码的Intel 8086(386)汇编</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mov ax, cs // cs-&gt;ax, 目标操作数在前</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>GNU as汇编：产生32位代码，使用AT&amp;T系统V语法</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">movl var, %eax //(var) -&gt; %eax</span><br><span class=\"line\">movb -4(%ebp), %al //取出一字节</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>内嵌汇编，gcc编译x.c会产生中间结果as汇编文件x.s</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">__asm__(&quot;汇编语句&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">:输出</span><br><span class=\"line\">:输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">:破坏部分描述);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">__asm__(&quot;movb %%fs:%2, %%al&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">:&quot;=a&quot;(_res)</span><br><span class=\"line\">:&quot;0&quot;(seg),&quot;m&quot;(*(addr))</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">0或空表示使用与相应输出一样的寄存器</span><br><span class=\"line\">a表示使用eax并编号%0</span><br><span class=\"line\">%2表示addr,m表示使用内存</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"after_page_tables\">after_page_tables<a title=\"#after_page_tables\" href=\"#after_page_tables\"></a></h3>\n<p>设置了页表之后</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">after_page_tables:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pushl $0</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pushl $0</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pushl $0</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pushl $L6</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pushl $_main //这几句代码相对于设置调用函数的栈帧</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jmp set_paging</span><br><span class=\"line\">L6:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  jmp L6</span><br><span class=\"line\">setuo_paging:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  设置页表 //之后学</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ret</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">setup_paging执行ret后会执行函数main() </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart10.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"进入main函数\">进入main函数<a title=\"#进入main函数\" href=\"#进入main函数\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>三个参数分别是envp，argv，argc，但此处main并没有使用（返回时因为有三个参数所以地址要+6，但main永远不会返回）</li>\n<li>main的工作就是xx_init:内存、中断、设备、时钟、CPU等内容的初始化</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mem_init(); <span class=\"comment\">//内存初始化</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  trap_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  blk_dev_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  chr_dev_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  tty_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  time_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sched_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  buffer_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  hd_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  floppy_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sti();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  move_to_user_mode();</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(!fork())&#123;init();&#125; <span class=\"comment\">//永远不会退出，所以永远不会返回L6执行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart11.png\" alt=\"Untitled\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">mem_init</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">long</span> start_mem, <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> end_mem)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; PAGING_PAGES; ++i)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mem_map[i] = USED;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  i = MAP_NR(start_mem);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  end_mem -= start_mem;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  end_mem &gt;&gt;= <span class=\"number\">12</span>; <span class=\"comment\">//4kB</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(end_mem-- &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mem_map[i++] = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"PeFile","link":"2022/02/19/PeFile"},"next":{"title":"EASYHOOK","link":"2022/01/28/EASYHOOK"},"plink":"https://bexh0lder.github.io/2022/01/28/OsStart/","toc":[{"id":"操作系统的启动","title":"操作系统的启动","index":"1","children":[{"id":"从图灵机到通用图灵机","title":"从图灵机到通用图灵机","index":"1.1"},{"id":"从通用图灵机到计算机","title":"从通用图灵机到计算机","index":"1.2"},{"id":"x86pc的开机过程","title":"x86PC的开机过程","index":"1.3"},{"id":"引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）","title":"引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）","index":"1.4","children":[{"id":"读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup","title":"读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup","index":"1.4.1"},{"id":"read_it-//读入system模块","title":"read_it &#x2F;&#x2F;读入system模块","index":"1.4.2"}]},{"id":"setup模块，即setup.s","title":"setup模块，即setup.s","index":"1.5","children":[{"id":"进入保护模式(变为32位，即1m-→-4gb)","title":"进入保护模式(变为32位，即1M → 4GB)","index":"1.5.1"},{"id":"jmpi-0,-8","title":"jmpi 0, 8","index":"1.5.2"},{"id":"cr0寄存器","title":"cr0寄存器","index":"1.5.3"},{"id":"保护模式下的地址翻译和中断处理","title":"保护模式下的地址翻译和中断处理","index":"1.5.4"}]},{"id":"跳到system模块执行","title":"跳到system模块执行","index":"1.6","children":[{"id":"head.s（32位汇编代码）","title":"head.s（32位汇编代码）","index":"1.6.1"},{"id":"after_page_tables","title":"after_page_tables","index":"1.6.2"},{"id":"进入main函数","title":"进入main函数","index":"1.6.3"}]}]}],"copyright":{"custom":"转载请标明作者:D"},"reading_time":"3188 字约 21 分钟"}